Selective Licensing Agreement

Chapter 1: General Provisions

Article 1: Definitions

Project: Includes the website (https://yfqqp.github.io/esmail.web/) and all its components
Source Code: Includes HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and used libraries
Personal Content: Includes images, texts, CV, personal experiences
Private Data: Personal information, contact details, experiences, personal projects

Article 2: License Scope

```
This agreement governs the use of "Esmail Web" project and precisely defines
what can be shared and what must be protected, balancing between
knowledge sharing and privacy protection.
```

---

Chapter 2: Technical Licensing Details

Article 3: Shareable Code

3.1 Allowed File Types:

```
- HTML files (page structure only)
- CSS files (design and styling)
- JavaScript files (functions and applications)
- Configuration files
- Technical documentation files
```

3.2 Code Usage Conditions:

¬∑ Usage: Allowed for personal, educational, commercial use
¬∑ Modification: Allowed to modify and improve code
¬∑ Distribution: Allowed to distribute original or modified code
¬∑ Requirement: Must credit original source in README file

3.3 Allowed Practical Examples:

```javascript
// ‚úì Allowed: Using JavaScript functions
function navigateToSection(sectionId) {
    // This code can be used
}

// ‚úì Allowed: Cloning CSS styles
