```

Article 4: Protected Personal Content

4.1 Protected Images:

```
- Personal portraits
- Family photos
- Personal screenshots
- Memorial photos
- Any image containing personal features
```

4.2 Protected Texts:

```
- Curriculum Vitae (CV)
- Personal work experiences
- Completed personal projects
- Personal biography (Bio)
- Certificates and recommendations
- Any text describing personal experience
```

4.3 Protected Data:

```
- Contact information
- Personal career history
- Acquired skills and experiences
- Personal achievements
- Any identifying data
```

