```

Article 8: Technical Protection Tips

8.1 Recommended Protection Settings:

```javascript
// Add warning in console
console.log("‚ö†Ô∏è Code is open source - Personal content is protected");

// Protect images with robots.txt
User-agent: *
Disallow: /images/personal/
Disallow: /assets/private/
```

8.2 Add Protection Metadata:

```html
<meta name="copyright" content="Code is open source - Personal content is protected">
<meta name="author" content="Esmail">
```

